  "contentData": [
    {
      "contentTypeKey": "e0c934fe-087e-4521-9176-9a0723b8b34c",
      "udi": "umb://element/e49913755a6340dabd031415ad7ffefe",
      "traction": [
        "Geographical"
      ],
      "descriptionOfEnablingFactor": "<p>Viet Nam has an abundant potential for solar energy. The Power Development Plan 8 estimates that Viet Nam has a solar energy potential of 963 GW (including a 77.4 GW potential for water PVs and 48.2 GW for rooftop solar).</p>"
    },
    {
      "contentTypeKey": "e0c934fe-087e-4521-9176-9a0723b8b34c",
      "udi": "umb://element/1ef5a6d721ca4909aeee70a28412c6ea",
      "traction": [
        "Market structure for business and finance"
      ],
      "descriptionOfEnablingFactor": "<p>A high-growth economy, Viet Nam has achieved an average GDP growth of 7% from 2010 to 2019, resulting in a high energy demand that has driven the government to prioritize ensuring a reliable energy supply.</p>"
    },
    {
      "contentTypeKey": "e0c934fe-087e-4521-9176-9a0723b8b34c",
      "udi": "umb://element/2ab1d7b4e84e4ef39799cf3b868aa043",
      "traction": [
        "Behavioural and socio-cultural"
      ],
      "descriptionOfEnablingFactor": "<p>Air pollutions in cities generated public opposition to pollutant projects, leading some provinces to oppose the building of new coal power plants.</p>"
    },
    {
      "contentTypeKey": "e0c934fe-087e-4521-9176-9a0723b8b34c",
      "udi": "umb://element/f166e3ae627942d0840db6f24681ab17",
      "traction": [
        "Institutional framework and governance structure"
      ],
      "descriptionOfEnablingFactor": "<p>International organization present in Viet Nam supported the deployment of PVs, for example the ADB through its Enhancing Readiness for Solar Power Deployment in Viet Nam project.</p>"
    },
    {
      "contentTypeKey": "e0c934fe-087e-4521-9176-9a0723b8b34c",
      "udi": "umb://element/81123b23cd11408ebe3cc9ada949d031",
      "traction": [
        "Market structure for business and finance"
      ],
      "descriptionOfEnablingFactor": "<p>Viet Nam has a flexible investing environment, allowing for the channelling of international financing. It did not set local content requirements as criteria for the FiT</p>"
    }
  ],
  "settingsData": []
}]]></Value>
